revision.text:
'''Side-entrance Sarcophagus Chamber''' (横口式石槨) refers to a type of horizontal stone burial structure observed in the later to terminal phases of the Kofun period. It is also known as '''sekkanshiki Sekishitsu''' (石棺式石室).
This type of burial chamber is constructed using cut stones, designed to house {{ill|wooden coffins|ja|木棺|1=Wooden Coffin|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|dry lacquer coffins|ja|乾漆棺|1=Kanshitsu coffin|12=draft|12=draft}}. The chamber features an opening on one of its shorter sides. In some cases, it includes an antechamber or {{ill|Endō|lt=passageway (sen-dō)|ja|羨道|1=endō|lt=endō (tomb entrance)|12=draft|12=draft}}.
The distribution of such burial structures is primarily concentrated in the {{ill|Kinai region|ja|畿内|12=draft|12=draft}}, with notable examples including the {{ill|Kannonzuka Kofun|ja|観音塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Habikino, Osaka|ja|羽曳野市|12=draft|12=draft}}, and the {{ill|Takamatsuzuka Kofun|ja|高松塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Asuka, Nara|ja|明日香村|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Major Kofun with Sekkaku-style Burial Chambers == * {{ill|Oni-no-Manaita and Oni-no-Secchin|ja|鬼の俎・鬼の雪隠|12=draft|12=draft}} (Asuka, Nara) * {{ill|Kengoshizuka Kofun|ja|牽牛子塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Asuka, Nara) * {{ill|Takamatsuzuka Kofun|ja|高松塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Asuka, Nara) * {{ill|Kitora Kofun|ja|キトラ古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Asuka, Nara) * {{ill|Nakaoyama Kofun|ja|中尾山古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Asuka, Nara) * {{ill|Takamiya Shrine Kofun|ja|束明神古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Takatori, Nara) * {{ill|Ishi-no-Karato Kofun|ja|石のカラト古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Nara City, Nara; Kizugawa, Kyoto) * {{ill|Shishiyotsuka Kofun|ja|シシヨツカ古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Kanan, Osaka) * {{ill|Koguchiyama Kofun|ja|小口山古墳|1=Koguchiyama Kofun|12=draft|12=draft}} (Habikino, Osaka) * {{ill|Hachibusuyama Nishimine Kofun|ja|鉢伏山西峰古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Habikino, Osaka) * {{ill|Kannonzuka Kofun|ja|観音塚古墳 (羽曳野市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Habikino, Osaka) * {{ill|Okameishi Kofun|ja|お亀石古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Tondabayashi, Osaka) * {{ill|Oichi No.1 Kofun|ja|尾市古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Fukuyama, Hiroshima) * {{ill|Inoko Kofun|ja|猪ノ子古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Fukuyama, Hiroshima) * {{ill|Soneda Shiratsuka Kofun|ja|曽根田白塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Fukuyama, Hiroshima) * {{ill|Kitazuka Kofun|ja|北塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Fukuyama, Hiroshima) * {{ill|Iwaya Kofun|ja|岩屋古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Yonago, Tottori) * {{ill|Danbara Kofun|ja|団原古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (Matsue, Shimane) * {{ill|Furumiya Kofun (Oita)|ja|古宮古墳 (大分市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Oita City, Oita)
